<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>This validator doesn't seem to work any more after upgrading to PHP5.3 (which now comes with fileinfo extension built in)</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$mime = new finfo(FILEINFO_MIME);
$this-&gt;_type = $mime-&gt;file($value);
</code></pre>

<p>file() used to return just "image/jpeg", now it returns "image/jpeg; charset=binary". This no longer matches values in the predefined array and validation fails.</p>

